## Failure.orDefault() method

Gets the value associated with a successful [result](./ts-utils.iresult.md)<!-- -->, or a default value if the corresponding operation failed.

**Signature:**

```typescript
orDefault(): T | undefined;
```
**Returns:**

T \| undefined

The return value, if the operation was successful, or `undefined` if an error occurs.
